Good Reference : 
https://gist.github.com/djoreilly/c5ea44663c133b246dd9d42b921f7646

sudo ovs-dpctl  dump-flows

Trace the table flow
-----------------------------------------------------------
sudo ovs-appctl ofproto/trace gtp_br0 in_port=gtp0

Monitor specific table espcially for IN/OUT
----------------------------------------------------------
sudo ovs-ofctl monitor gtp_br0 128 watch:table=3

Snoop on Bridge
------------------------------------------------------------
sudo ovs-ofctl snoop gtp_br0

Dump the hidden flows
--------------------------------------------------------------
ovs-appctl bridge/dump-flows uplink_br0

Dump Current Packet Flow
--------------------------------------------------------------
sudo ovs-dpctl dump-flows
